                  </hi>.—<hi rend="italic">He also</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
PLEADED GUILTY</hi>** <hi rend="italic">to having been before convicted in August</hi>, 1864.—<hi rend="italic">
